Modern Shogi - resources
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

May be subject of different licenses.

List:

- UI images - free - Google material design
- UI sound - proprietary, and buyed by the author, do not use them in your projects
- Models - all free and maded by author for now
- UI flags - free - borrowed and transformed from Wikipedia
- Fonts - Zekton called Modern(free), Rotonda Bold called Friendly(non-free but ok to use in free project such as Modern Shogi).

